text: Arleta Podolak (born 20 October 1993, in Warsaw)Polish 2016 Olympic team at the Polish Olympic Committee website is a Polish judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 57 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the first round by Lien Chen-ling. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Poland Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw Category:European Games competitors for Poland Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games
